PrecisAppointment of The Honourable LANCE S.G. FINCH, Chief Justice of British Columbia, as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of BRITISH COLUMBIA, who shall, during pleasure, execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of British Columbia during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
